        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I got this to \"work\" (crash):\n```sh\nrm -rf build && CMAKE_EXTRA_FLAGS=\"-DCMAKE_C_COMPILER=clang -DENABLE_ASAN_UBSAN=1 -DCMAKE_C_FLAGS=-fsanitize=object-size\" make CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=RelWithDebInfo\n```\n(without `CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=RelWithDebInfo` I was getting the warning `clang: warning: the object size sanitizer has no effect at -O0, but is explicitly enabled: -fsanitize=object-size [-Winvalid-command-line-argument]`)",
